gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 102, Celtics 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Celtics, 102-100, as they snapped Bostons franchise-best 20-0 at home start to the season. Jamal Murray (35 points, eight rebounds, five assists) and Nikola Jokic (34 points, 12 rebounds, nine assists) totaled 69 of the Nuggets 102 points. Derrick White led the Celtics with 24 points, three rebounds, and five assists as Jayson Tatum (22 points, eight rebounds, five assists) and Kristaps Porzingis (21 points, eight rebounds) added 43 points.
